      "description": "Looking for your next great project? This car has tons of character and is the perfect candidate for a full restoration! While it currently needs significant mechanical work and cosmetic TLC, it offers a solid foundation for anyone who loves bringing a classic back to life. It\u2019s an honest, high-potential vehicle ready for a dedicated new owner to uncover its former glory!",
